Business Brief -- Nichols Institute:
   Company to Report Loss
   After Charge for Quarter
The restructuring will integrate and consolidate the
company's laboratory operations in El Paso, Houston, San
Antonio and Dallas. Nichols said it plans to swap 225,000
Class C common shares for its joint venture partners'
interest in the Dallas facility. No agreement has been signed
with those partners, the company said.
   Nichols runs clinical testing services and related
research and development operations.